name: Golden Pineapple - Audio Trip VR
description:
Audio Trip is a VR dance game developed by Kinemotik Studios. It was released in 2019 and this song was the first to be added as a dlc level after the original setlist. The notes & stage have been removed to fully display the visualizer that plays during the track.

Music by Tolan
Visual by Kinemotik Studios - twitter @AudioTripVR

Duration: 02:41

-Audio for personal use only-
